{"title_page": "Go Soo-jung", "text_new": "{{Short description|South Korean actress and model}}\n{{Korean name|Go}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Goo Soo Jung\n| image              =\n| birth_name         = Goo Soo-Jung\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1995|4|17|df=y}}\n| birth_place        = [[South Korea]]\n| death_place        = {{death date and age|2020|2|7|1995|4|17}}\n| nationality        = [[Demographics of South Korea|South Korean]]\n| other_names        = Go, Soo Jung\n| citizenship        = [[Demographics of South Korea|South Korean]]\n| education          = \n| occupation         = Actress, Model\n| agency             = Story J Company\n| years_active       = 2016\u20132020\n| known_for          = ''[[Solomon's Perjury (TV series)|Solomon's Perjury]]'' <br /> ''[[Guardian: The Lonely and Great God|Goblin]]''\n}}\n\n'''Goo Soo-jung''' (April 17, 1995 \u2013 February 7, 2020) was a South Korean actress and model. She was best known for starring in [[Guardian: The Lonely and Great God|Goblin]] and [[Solomon's Perjury (TV series)|Solomon's Perjury]]. She also appeared in a music video for BTS's song With Seoul.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.news1.kr/articles/?3841113|title=\uace0\uc218\uc815, \uc9c0\ubcd1 \ub1cc\uc885\uc591 25\uc138 \uc0ac\ub9dd\u2026\ucd94\ubaa8 \ubb3c\uacb0 \uc9c0\uc18d(\uc885\ud569)|publisher=News1|date=January 1, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20200212_0000916411&cID=10601&pID=10600|title=\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uace0\uc218\uc815 \uc0ac\ub9dd, \ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8 MV \uc8fc\uc778\uacf5 :: \uacf5\uac10\uc5b8\ub860 \ub274\uc2dc\uc2a4\ud1b5\uc2e0\uc0ac|publisher=Newsis|date=January 2, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/202002120232H|title=\uace0\uc218\uc815, 25\uc138 \ubcc4\uc774 \uc9c0\ub2e4\u2026\"\ub09c \uad1c\ucc2e\uc544\"\ub77c\ub354\ub2c8|publisher=Hankyung|date=January 3, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1111308301|title=\uc2e0\uc778 \ubc30\uc6b0 \uace0\uc218\uc815, \ud5a5\ub144 25\uc138 \uc694\uc808..\uc18c\uc18d\uc0ac \"\ubc1d\uc740 \ubbf8\uc18c \uc601\uc6d0\ud788 \uae30\uc5b5\ud560 \uac83\"|publisher=OSEN|date=January 4, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Biography==\nGoo Soo-jung was born on April 17, 1995. She started her acting career in 2016 and she also did modeling. She did supporting in dramas such as [[Guardian: The Lonely and Great God|Goblin]] and [[Solomon's Perjury (TV series)|Solomon's Perjury]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.news1.kr/articles/?3840253|title=\ubc30\uc6b0 \uace0\uc218\uc815, 25\uc138\ub85c \uc694\uc808\u2026\ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8\u00b7\uacf5\uc720\uc640\ub3c4 \uc778\uc5f0 \ub208\uae38|publisher=News1|date=January 5, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1111308390|title=\uc138\uc0c1 \ub5a0\ub09c \u6545\uace0\uc218\uc815 \ub204\uad6c?..'\ub3c4\uae68\ube44'\ub85c \ub370\ubdd4\ud55c '\ub108\ubb34 \uc77c\ucc0d \uc9c4 \uaf43'(\uc885\ud569)[Oh!\uc388 \uc774\uc288&#93;|publisher=OSEN|date=January 6, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/202002120007I|title=\ubc30\uc6b0 \uace0\uc218\uc815 25\uc138 \ub098\uc774\ub85c \uc0ac\ub9dd\u2026\uc18c\uc18d\uc0ac \"\uc601\uc6d0\ud788 \uae30\uc5b5\ud560 \uac83\"|publisher=Hankyung|date=March 1, 2020}}</ref>\n\n===Death===\nGoo Soo-jung died on February 7, 2020. Her agency Story J Company stated that she passed away due to chronic illness. Her parents held the funeral privately.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/2020021318387|title=\ubc30\uc6b0 \uace0\uc218\uc815 \uc0ac\ub9dd\u2026\ud5a5\ub144 25\uc138|publisher=Hankyung|date=March 2, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newspim.com/news/view/20200212000666|title=\ub274\uc2a4\ud54c - \ubc30\uc6b0 \uace0\uc218\uc815 \ud5a5\ub144 25\uc138 \uc0ac\ub9dd\u2026\uc601\uc6d0\ud788 \uae30\uc5b5\ud560 \uac83|publisher=Newspim|date=March 3, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asiatoday.co.kr/view.php?key=20200212001130381|title=\u2018\ub3c4\uae68\ube44\u2019 \ubc30\uc6b0 \uace0\uc218\uc815, \uc0ac\ub9dd\u2026\uc18c\uc18d\uc0ac \uc601\uc6d0\ud788 \uae30\uc5b5\ud558\uaca0\ub2e4 - \uc544\uc2dc\uc544\ud22c\ub370\uc774|publisher=Asia Today|date=March 4, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hankyung.com/life/article/202002120685H|title=\"\uace0\uc218\uc815 \uc9c0\ubcd1\uc740 \ub1cc\uc885\uc591, \uc9c0\ub09c\ud574\ubd80\ud130 \uc544\ud320\uc5b4\uc694\"|publisher=Hankyung|date=March 5, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2020021306120342987|title=\uace0\uc218\uc815 \uc9c0\ubcd1\uc740 \ub1cc\uc885\uc591, \uc9c0\ub09c\ud574\ubd80\ud130 \uc544\ud320\uc5b4\uc694|publisher=StarNews|date=March 5, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gukjenews.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=1240298|title=\uace0\uc218\uc815, \uaf43\ub2e4\uc6b4 \ub098\uc774\uc5d0 \ub5a0\ub098..\u2018\uadf8\uacf3\uc5d0\uc120 \uc548\uc2dd\ub9cc \uc788\uae30\ub97c\u2019 - \uad6d\uc81c\ub274\uc2a4<|publisher=International News|date=March 6, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title!! Role!! Notes !! Ref.\n|-\n|2016|| ''[[Guardian: The Lonely and Great God|Goblin]]'' ||Ghost || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1111308332|title=\uc2a4\ud1a0\ub9ac\uc81c\uc774\ucef4\ud37c\ub2c8 \"\u6545 \uace0\uc218\uc815, \ub204\uad6c\ubcf4\ub2e4 \uc21c\uc218\ud558\uace0 \ube5b\ub098\ub294 \uc0ac\ub78c\"|publisher=OSEN|date=March 7, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2016|| ''[[Solomon's Perjury (TV series)|Solomon's Perjury]]'' ||Girl reading a memorial service || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.news1.kr/articles/?3840537|title='\uc0ac\ub9dd' \uace0\uc218\uc815\u2026\ubc29\ud0c4\uc18c\ub144\ub2e8 \ubba4\ube44 \ucd9c\uc5f0+'\ub3c4\uae68\ube44'\ub85c \ub370\ubdd4|publisher=News1|date=March 8, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===Music Videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\