oday|date=January 17, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014|| ''[[Pinocchio (2014 TV series)|Pinocchio]]'' ||Jo Dae Gook || Guest role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://bntnews.hankyung.com/apps/news?popup=0&nid=04&c1=04&c2=04&c3=00&nkey=201504271839023&mode=sub_view|title=\u2018\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015\u2019 \uc138\uac15\uace0 2\ud559\ub1443\ubc18, \ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80 \uacf5\uac1c\uc640 \ud568\uaed8 \ubca0\uc77c \ubc97\ub294\ub2e4|publisher=BNT News|date=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015|| ''[[Who Are You: School 2015]]'' ||Seung-ho || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newspim.com/news/view/20150616000153|title=\uc6d4\ud654\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 '\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015' 2\ud559\ub144 3\ubc18 \ub2e8\uccb4\uc0ac\uc9c4 \uacf5\uac1c\u2026\"\uc218\uace0\ud588\uc5b4\uc694. \uc78a\uc9c0 \uc54a\uc744\uac8c\"|publisher=Newspim|date=January 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015|| ''[[Oh My Venus]]'' ||Kim Yeong Joon || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://stoo.asiae.co.kr/article.php?aid=13067647710|title=\ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80\ub85c \ubbf8\ub9ac \ubcf4\ub294 '\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015'[\uc2a4\ud3ec\uce20\ud22c\ub370\uc774]|publisher=Sports Today|date=January 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year!! Title !! Role !! Language !! Notes !! Ref. \n|-\n| 2015||''[[Wonderful Nightmare]]''||Kyeong Ho || Korean || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvdaily.asiae.co.kr/read.php3?aid=1430132357894060016|title='\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad50 2015' \uc6b0\ub9ac \ubc18\uc5d0 \uc774\ub7f0 \uc560\ub4e4 \uaf2d \uc788\ub2e4 '\uc138\uac15\uace0 \ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80 \uacf5\uac1c'|publisher=TV Daily|date=January 29, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015||''[[The Chronicles of Evil]]''|| || Korean || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://tenasia.hankyung.com/topic/article/2015042796664|title='\ud6c4\uc544\uc720 \ud559\uad502015' \ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80 \uacf5\uac1c..\uc2e4\uc81c \uad50\uc2e4 \uac19\uc544 '\ub9ac\uc5bc+\uacf5\uac10'|publish