8\uc5d0 \uc774\ub7f0 \uc560\ub4e4 \uaf2d \uc788\ub2e4 '\uc138\uac15\uace0 \ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80 \uacf5\uac1c'|publisher=TV Daily|date=January 5, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2015/04/401882|title=\ud765\ud589\ubd88\ud328 \u2018\ud559\uad502015\u2019, \uc624\ub298(27\uc77c) \ubca0\uc77c \ubc97\ub294\ub2e4|publisher=Maeil Economy|date=January 2, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title!! Role!! Notes !! Ref.\n|-\n|2012|| ''[[Operation Proposal]]'' || || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2015/04/401882|title=\ud765\ud589\ubd88\ud328 \u2018\ud559\uad502015\u2019, \uc624\ub298(27\uc77c) \ubca0\uc77c \ubc97\ub294\ub2e4|publisher=Daily Economy|date=January 27, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2013|| ''[[Golden Rainbow (TV series)|Golden Rainbow]]'' ||Seo Tae Yeong (Young) || Guest role || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tvreport.co.kr/728899|title=\ud6c4\uc544\uc720 \ud559\uad502015, 2\ud559\ub144 3\ubc18 \uc778\uc99d\uc0f7 \"\uc78a\uc9c0 \uc54a\uc744\uac8c\"|publisher=TV Report|date=January 7, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014|| ''[[Gap-dong]]'' ||Kim Shin Yong || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.topstarnews.net/news/articleView.html?idxno=124620|title=\u2018\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad50 2015\u2019, \uc6b0\ub9ac \ubc18\uc5d0 \uc788\uc744 \ubc95\ud55c \u2018\uc2f1\ud06c\ub85c\uc728\u2019 \ub3cb\ub294 \uad50\uc6b0 \uad00\uacc4\ub3c4 ...|publisher=Top Star News|date=January 10, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014|| ''[[Flower Grandpa Investigation Unit]]'' ||Jung Myung Ho (Young)  || Guest role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvdaily.asiae.co.kr/read.php3?aid=1434418945924657017#rs|title=\u2018\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015\u2019 2\ud559\ub144 3\ubc18 \ub2e8\uccb4\uc0ac\uc9c4 \u201c\uc5b4\ub290\ub367 \ub9c8\uc9c0\ub9c9 \ud68c, \uc78a\uc9c0 \uc54a\uc744\uac8c\u201d|publisher=TV Daily|date=January 14, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014|| ''[[Blade Man]]'' ||Yoon Seok  || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etoday.co.kr/news/view/1144942|title=\uc6d4\ud654\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 \u2018\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad50 2015\u2019 \uc138\uac15\uace0 2\ud559\ub144 3\ubc18 \ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80 \uacf5\uac1c\u2026\uae40\uc18c\ud604\u318d\ub0a8\uc8fc\ud601\u318d\uc721\uc131\uc7ac \u5916 \uc778\ubb3c \uc81c\ub300\ub85c \uc54c\uae30|publisher=E Today|date=January 17, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014|| ''[[Pinocchio (2014 TV series)|Pinocchio]]'' ||Jo Dae Gook || Guest role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://bntnews.hankyung.com/apps/news?popup=0&nid=04&c1=04&c2=04&c3=00&nkey=201504271839023&mode=sub_view|title=\u2018\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015\u2019 \uc138\uac15\uace0 2\ud559\ub1443\ubc18, \ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80 \uacf5\uac1c\uc640 \ud568\uaed8 \ubca0\uc77c \ubc97\ub294\ub2e4|publisher=BNT News|date=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015|| ''[[Who Are You: School 2015]]'' ||Seung-ho || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newspim.com/news/view/20150616000153|title=\uc6d4\ud654\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 '\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015' 2\ud559\ub144 3\ubc18 \ub2e8\uccb4\uc0ac\uc9c4 \uacf5\uac1c\u2026\"\uc218\uace0\ud588\uc5b4\uc694. \uc78a\uc9c0 \uc54a\uc744\uac8c\"|publisher=Newspim|date=January 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015|| ''[[Oh My Venus]]'' ||Kim Yeong Joon || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://stoo.asiae.co.kr/article.php?aid=13067647710|title=\ucd9c\uc11d\ubd80\ub85c \ubbf8\ub9ac \ubcf4\ub294 '\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad502015'[\uc2a4\ud3ec\uce20\ud22c\ub370\uc774]|publisher=Sports Today|date=January 24, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year!! Title !! Role !! Language !! Notes !! Ref. \n|-\n| 2015||''[[Wonderful Nightmare]]''||Kyeong Ho || Korean || Supporting role || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvdaily.asiae.co.kr/read.php3?aid=1430132357894060016|title='\ud6c4\uc544\uc720-\ud559\uad50 2015' \uc6b0\ub9ac \ubc18\uc5d0 \uc774\ub7f0 \uc560\ub4e4 \uaf2d \uc788\ub2e4 '\uc138\uac15\uace0 \